| 
| Meta-type for a literal String value, for which `type` is fixed to the `BMM_TYPE`
| representing `String` and `value` is of type `String`.
| 

class BMM_STRING_VALUE
    is_a BMM_PRIMITIVE_VALUE<>

feature_group ("access")

    | 
    | Native String value.
    | 
    prop value: String;


end
